      <title>拜登称他可能有权自行关闭边境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/biden-says-he-may-have-authority-to-close-border-on-his-own</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，他仍在考虑采取单方面行动关闭美国南部边境，并研究他是否有法律权力在未经国会批准的情况下这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/biden-says-he-may-have-authority-to-close-border-on-his-own</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 03:45:33 GMT</pubDate>
