      <title>韩国在总统公投中投票支持议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/south-korea-votes-for-new-parliament-in-referendum-on-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国民众在尹锡烈总统任期内举行的唯一一次全民公投中选举新议会，这将决定他在剩余三年任期内将拥有多少权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/south-korea-votes-for-new-parliament-in-referendum-on-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 21:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
